    "Now, focusing on the p T -integrated results, we jointly examine v 1 and v 2.",
    "The collision energy dependence of directed and elliptic flow is summarized in Fig. 14, where panel (a) shows the slope of the p T -integrated directed flow at midrapidity, dv 1 ∕dy|y = 0, for, K, p, Λ, and multi-strange hadrons and Ξ -from Au+Au collisions in the 10-40% centrality interval.",
